%3A1739517641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F6e4e%2Flive%2F6fdb7580-ea88-11ef-b261-bbdf17c85eb4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc8d9z68grn3o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22January's%20wildfires%20have%20exacerbated%20the%20decline%20of%20Hollywood's%20once%20booming%20film%20and%20television%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc8d9z68grn3o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc8d9z68grn3o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc8d9z68grn3o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%2C%20Trump's%20Big%20Nuclear%20Push%20To%20Get%20More%20Atomic%20Reactors%20To%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20energy%20security%20on%20their%20minds%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20have%20affirmed%20their%20faith%20in%20atomic%20energy.%20After%20their%20talks%20at%20the%20White%20House%20on%20Thursday%2C%20they%20reinforced%20their%20commitment%20to%20work%20together%20on%20US-designed%20nuclear%20reactors%20in%20India%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20large-scale%20localisation%20and%20possible%20technology%20transfer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202008%2C%20when%20the%20landmark%20India-US%20Civilian%20Nuclear%20Deal%20was%20signed%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20headway%20in%20negotiations.%20No%20new%20American%20nuclear%20reactor%20ever%20made%20it%20to%20Indian%20soil%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%20Seeking%20to%20end%20the%20stalemate%2C%20the%20leaders%20have%20now%20shown%20interest%20in%20not%20only%20building%20large%20reactors%20but%20also%20advanced%20small%20modular%20reactors%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-in-us-donald-trump-inside-pm-modi-trump-meet-5th-gen-fighters-mission-500-26-11-convict-7706859%5C%22%3EInside%20PM%20Modi-Trump%20Meet%3A%205th%20Gen%20Jets%2C%2026%2F11%20Extradition%2C%20'Mission%20500'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stumbling%20block%20has%20been%20India's%20people-friendly%20nuclear%20liability%20regime%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20bugbear%20for%20American%20nuclear%20suppliers.%20Most%20global%20nuclear%20damage%20liability%20regimes%20are%20friendlier%20to%20commercial%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20joint%20statement%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Trump%20welcomed%20Budget%202025%20announcements%20to%20amend%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Act%20and%20Civil%20Liability%20for%20Nuclear%20Damage%20Act%20(CLNDA)%20for%20nuclear%20reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20the%20two%20leaders%20also%20%26quot%3Bdecided%20to%20establish%20bilateral%20arrangements%20in%20accordance%20with%20CLNDA%2C%20that%20would%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20civil%20liability%20and%20facilitate%20the%20collaboration%20of%20Indian%20and%20US%20industry%20in%20the%20production%20and%20deployment%20of%20nuclear%20reactors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20while%20in%20opposition%20in%202010%20-%20when%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20-%20made%20sure%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeople-friendly%26quot%3B%20provisions%20were%20incorporated%20into%20the%20CLNDA.%20Now%2C%20one%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20how%20the%20amendments%20are%20made%20which%20can%20reconcile%20both%20American%20and%20Indian%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-energy-week-nuclear-power-to-be-part-of-all-energy-talks-minister-hardeep-singh-puri-ahead-of-pms-us-visit-7686176%5C%22%3ENuclear%20Power%20To%20Be%20Part%20Of%20All%20Energy%20Talks%3A%20Minister%20Ahead%20Of%20PM's%20US%20Visit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussians%20are%20already%20working%20on%20additional%20reactors%20at%20Kudankulam%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20proceeded%20with%20it%20even%20after%20India%20passed%20the%20new%20nuclear%20liability%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20understanding%20between%20leaders%20may%20just%20open%20doors%20for%20American%20suppliers%20to%20make%20reactors%20on%20Indian%20soil.%20Westinghouse%20Electric%20Company%20has%20been%20negotiating%20to%20sell%20AP%201000%20nuclear%20reactors%20to%20India.%20New%20Delhi%20had%20also%20identified%20a%20Greenfield%20site%20to%20build%20these%20large%20passively%20cooled%20reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20and%20Westinghouse%20have%20also%20been%20discussing%20a%20project%20to%20build%20six%201%2C000-MW%20nuclear%20reactors%20at%20Kovvada%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20anvil%20are%20also%20the%20small%20and%20modular%20nuclear%20reactors%20that%20have%20gained%20traction%20in%20recent%20times.%20In%20his%20meeting%20with%20US%20Security%20Advisor%20Michael%20Waltz%20too%2C%20PM%20Modi%20discussed%20industrial%20cooperation%20and%20civil%20nuclear%20energy%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20small%20modular%20reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Trump%20said%20the%20path%20forward%20for%20enhanced%20civil%20nuclear%20cooperation%20will%20unlock%20plans%20to%20build%20large%20US-designed%20reactors%20and%20enable%20collaboration%20to%20develop%2C%20deploy%2C%20and%20scale%20up%20nuclear%20power%20generation%20with%20advanced%20small%20modular%20reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fgovernment-to-open-nuclear-power-sector-for-private-participation-7612362%5C%22%3EGovernment%20To%20Open%20Nuclear%20Power%20Sector%20For%20Private%20Participation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWrapping%20up%20the%20PM's%20US%20trip%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20said%20there%20was%20an%20agreement%20to%20realise%20the%20potential%20in%20civil%20nuclear%20energy%2C%20building%20US-designed%20nuclear%20reactors%20in%20India%2C%20and%20taking%20forward%20that%20process%20also%20through%20large-scale%20localization%20as%20well%20as%20technology%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20countries%20have%20been%20discussing%20for%20some%20time%2C%20cooperation%20in%20small%20modular%20reactors%20and%20that%20is%20again%20something%20that%20was%20flagged%20today.%20The%20obstacles%20in%20realizing%20this%20cooperation%20in%20previous%20years%20on%20account%20of%20some%20of%20the%20legal%20provisions%20that%20have%20remained%20in%20place%20in%20India%20have%20already%20begun%20to%20be%20addressed.%20You%20would%20have%20noticed%20the%20announcements%20that%20have%20been%20made%20in%20the%20budget%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20and%20we%20imagine%20that%20progress%20on%20these%20issues%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20realize%20the%20promise%20of%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20in%20this%20very%20important%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20rapprochement%20follows%20a%20Budget%20announcement%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20about%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20'Nuclear%20Energy%20Mission%20for%20Viksit%20Bharat'%20and%20a%20push%20for%20amending%20laws%20that%20are%20limiting%20this%20growth.%20In%20her%20speech%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20the%20development%20of%20at%20least%20100%20GW%20of%20nuclear%20energy%20by%202047%20is%20%26quot%3Bessential%20for%20our%20energy%20transition%20efforts%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-major-push-for-nuclear-power-india-asks-states-to-set-up-reactors-7005942%5C%22%3EIn%20Major%20Push%20For%20Nuclear%20Power%2C%20India%20Asks%20States%20To%20Set%20Up%20Reactors%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20an%20active%20partnership%20with%20the%20private%20sector%20towards%20this%20goal%2C%20amendments%20to%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Act%20and%20the%20Civil%20Liability%20for%20Nuclear%20Damage%20Act%20will%20be%20taken%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20end-to-end%20capabilities%20in%20nuclear%20technology%20-%20from%20uranium%20mining%20to%20making%20atomic%20power%20plants%20to%20reprocessing%20nuclear%20fuel.%20However%2C%20there%20aren't%20enough%20uranium%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtomic%20energy%20is%20considered%20the%20only%20sustainable%20almost%20zero%20carbon%20emission%20source%20for%20supplying%20base%20load%20power%2C%20which%20is%20why%20many%20countries%20are%20embracing%20nuclear%20energy%20to%20mitigate%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20even%20as%20they%20generate%20more%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20has%20also%20said%20that%20a%20'Nuclear%20Energy%20Mission%20for%20research%20%26amp%3B%20development%20of%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors%20(SMR)'%20with%20an%20outlay%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20set%20up.%20At%20least%20five%20indigenously%20developed%20SMRs%20will%20be%20operationalised%20by%202033%2C%20she%20said%20while%20presenting%20her%20record%20eighth%20consecutive%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20AK%20Mohanty%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%2C%20had%20earlier%20told%20NDTV%20that%20100%20GW%20by%202047%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20achievable%26quot%3B%20as%20India%20now%20has%20the%20technical%20capability.%20%26quot%3BBut%20getting%20land%20and%20appropriate%20atomic%20fuel%20could%20be%20a%20limiting%20factor.%20The%20private%20sector%20can%20help%20augment%20capacity%20by%20building%20captive%20atomic%20plants%20especially%20small%20modular%20reactors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20so%20far%20installed%20a%20capacity%20of%208%2C180%20MW%20of%20nuclear%20power%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%2C%20and%20presently%2C%20the%20country%20has%2024%20operating%20reactors.%20Among%20these%2C%2020%20reactors%20are%20Pressurised%20Heavy%20Water%20Reactors%20(PHWRs)%20and%20four%20are%20Light%20Water%20Reactors%20(LWRs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20being%20a%20very%20heavy%20energy%20consumer%20is%20now%20eyeing%20nuclear%20energy%20due%20to%20the%20low%20carbon%20source%20of%20base%20power%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739517420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7cv7828_kakrapar-atomic-power-station-gujarat-ani_625x300_21_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-trumps-big-nuclear-push-to-get-more-atomic-reactors-to-india-7707994%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20energy%20security%20on%20their%20minds%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20have%20affirmed%20their%20faith%20in%20atomic%20energy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-trumps-big-nuclear-push-to-get-more-atomic-reactors-to-india-7707994%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rehnaa%20Hai%20Terre%20Dil%20Mein%3A%20Saif%2C%20Maddy%2C%20Dia%20get%20nostalgic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739517044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118238324%2Cimgsize-103.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frevisit-rehnaa-hai-terre-dil-mein-on-valentines-day-saif-ali-khan-r-madhavan-dia-mirza-get-nostalgic-about-love-music-magic%2Farticleshow%2F118238242.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118238242.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERehnaa%20Hai%20Terre%20Dil%20Mein%2C%20a%202001%20romantic%20drama%2C%20gained%20