uts%20to%20federal%20spending%2C%20scaling%20back%20the%20size%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce%20and%20accessing%20agency%20data%20and%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Musk's%20seemingly%20limitless%20and%20unchecked%20power%20to%20strip%20the%20government%20of%20its%20workforce%20and%20eliminate%20entire%20departments%20with%20the%20stroke%20of%20a%20pen%20or%20click%20of%20a%20mouse%20would%20have%20been%20shocking%20to%20those%20who%20won%20this%20country's%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20Democratic%20state%20attorneys%20general%20wrote%20in%20their%20complaint.%20Musk%2C%20who%20was%20never%20elected%20or%20confirmed%2C%20has%20been%20given%20authority%20that's%20only%20reserved%20for%20the%20president%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20and%20US%20Justice%20Department%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20faced%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20lawsuits%20over%20the%20past%20three%20weeks%20challenging%20access%20by%20Musk%20and%20DOGE%20to%20records%20and%20internal%20systems%20at%20a%20number%20of%20agencies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20deferred%20resignation%20program%20offered%20to%20federal%20workers%20that%20mirrors%20an%20offer%20Musk%20made%20to%20employees%20of%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20then%20Twitter%2C%20when%20he%20bought%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20created%20DOGE%20via%20a%20Jan.%2020%20executive%20order%20that%20reorganized%20an%20existing%20White%20House%20office%2C%20the%20US%20Digital%20Service%2C%20and%20officially%20tasked%20the%20team%20with%20modernizing%20technology%20across%20government.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20he%20expanded%20its%20role%20to%20include%20oversight%20of%20spending%20and%20personnel%20cuts%20at%20federal%20agencies.%20Musk%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20hired%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20government%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20designation%20for%20workers%20who%20aren't%20expected%20to%20work%20more%20than%20130%20days%20per%20year%20in%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20lawsuits%20argue%20that%20Musk%20is%20operating%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bprincipal%20officer%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20a%20role%20that%20has%20to%20be%20filled%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20advice%20and%20consent%20of%20the%20Senate%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20Constitution's%20Appointments%20Clause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20brought%20by%2014%20Democratic%20state%20attorneys%20general%20in%20Washington%20accuses%20DOGE%20of%20exercising%20powers%20that%20Congress%20hasn't%20authorized.%20They%20invoke%20a%20legal%20principle%20known%20as%20the%20major-questions%20doctrine%20that%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court's%20conservative%20majority%20used%20to%20curb%20federal%20power%20when%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20president.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20states%20pointed%20to%20the%20court's%20use%20of%20that%20doctrine%20in%202022%2C%20when%20it%20tossed%20out%20a%20Biden%20administration%20rule%20that%20would%20have%20required%2080%20million%20workers%20to%20get%20Covid-19%20shots%20or%20periodic%20tests.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20justices%20said%20in%20that%20ruling%20that%20courts%20%26quot%3Bexpect%20Congress%20to%20speak%20clearly%20when%20authorizing%20an%20agency%20to%20exercise%20powers%20of%20vast%20economic%20and%20political%20significance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20case%20was%20filed%20in%20Maryland%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20group%20of%20current%20and%20former%20unnamed%20federal%20employees%20and%20contractors%20with%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20who%20say%20they've%20been%20directly%20affected%20by%20DOGE's%20efforts%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20agency%20records%20and%20the%20administration's%20suspension%20of%20the%20USAID's%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cases%20are%20New%20Mexico%20v.%20Musk%2C%2025-cv-429%2C%20US%20District%20Court%2C%20District%20of%20Columbia%2C%20and%20Doe%20v.%20Musk%2C%2025-cv-462%2C%20US%20District%20Court%2C%20Maryland%20(Greenbelt).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739516880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fib2urti8_musk-white-house-afp_625x300_12_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-power-in-trumps-government-is-challenged-in-court-7708101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20is%20facing%20the%20most%20direct%20legal%20challenge%20over%20the%20role%20he's%20assumed%20in%20the%20US%20government%2C%20with%20Democratic%20state%20officials%20and%20federal%20employees%20claiming%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20unconstitutionally%20delegated%20vast%20powers%20to%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-power-in-trumps-government-is-challenged-in-court-7708101%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Director%20of%20Berlin%20Film%20%E2%80%98Little%20Trouble%20Girls%E2%80%99%20Lines%20Up%20Witch%20Trial%20Drama%20%E2%80%98Veronika%20of%20Desenice%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Wild%20Woman%2C%E2%80%99%20About%20the%20Acting%20Process%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739516502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FLittle-Trouble-Girls.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236306545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Slovenian%20director%20Ur%C5%A1ka%20Djuki%C4%87%2C%20whose%20feature%20directorial%20debut%2C%20%E2%80%9CLittle%20Trouble%20Girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20makes%20its%20world%20premiere%20Feb.%2014%20as%20the%20opening%20film%20of%20Berlinale%E2%80%99s%20Perspectives%20section%2C%20is%20developing%20two%20new%20projects%2C%20she%20has%20told%20Variety.%20The%20projects%20are%20being%20produced%20by%20Djuki%C4%87%20through%20her%20p