0affected%20by%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs.%20India's%20high%20tariff%20rates%2C%20which%20average%209.5%25%20on%20US%20exports%20compared%20to%20the%20US's%203%25%20tariff%20rate%20on%20Indian%20goods%2C%20make%20it%20vulnerable%20to%20retaliatory%20tariffs.%20According%20to%20Nomura%20analysts%2C%20India's%20weighted%20average%20effective%20tariff%20on%20US%20exports%20is%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20US's%20tariff%20rate%20on%20Indian%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20also%20said%20that%20India%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhard%20place%20to%20do%20business%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20high%20tariffs.%20%26quot%3BBut%20again%2C%20whatever%20they%20charge%20us%2C%20we're%20charging%20them.%20So%2C%20it%20works%20out%20very%20well.%20It's%20a%20beautiful%2C%20simple%20system%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20charging%20too%20much%20or%20too%20little%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20these%20tariffs%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20far-reaching%2C%20with%20India's%20food%20products%2C%20vegetables%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20clothing%20sectors%20likely%20to%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest.%20Electrical%20machinery%2C%20gems%20and%20jewelry%2C%20pharma%20products%2C%20autos%2C%20iron%20and%20steel%20are%20also%20among%20the%20key%20commodities%20that%20India%20exports%20to%20the%20US%2C%20which%20could%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20developments%2C%20India%20is%20considering%20reducing%20tariffs%20on%20over%2030%20products%20and%20increasing%20its%20imports%20of%20US%20defense%20and%20energy%20goods%20to%20ease%20trade%20tensions.%20However%2C%20India's%20trade%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%20is%20complex%2C%20and%20the%20tariffs%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20for%20businesses%20and%20consumers%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mr%20Trump%20pushes%20ahead%20with%20his%20reciprocal%20tariff%20plans%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20among%20the%20hardest%20hit.%20With%20the%20tariffs%20potentially%20taking%20effect%20from%20April%20this%20year%2C%20India%20is%20bracing%20itself%20for%20the%20impact%20on%20its%20economy%20and%20trade%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20have%20broader%20implications%20for%20global%20trade.%20The%20move%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20US%20trade%20policy%2C%20which%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20for%20trade%20relationships%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20the%20tariffs%20are%20likely%20to%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20consumers%20and%20reduced%20competitiveness%20for%20businesses.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20the%20move%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20balanced%20trade%20relationship%20between%20the%20US%20and%20its%20trading%20partners.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739516280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7jivra5g_modi-trump-reuters_625x300_14_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-to-be-hit-hard-by-donald-trumps-reciprocal-tariffs-heres-why-7708057%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20impact%20of%20these%20tariffs%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20far-reaching%2C%20with%20India's%20food%20products%2C%20vegetables%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20clothing%20sectors%20likely%20to%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-to-be-hit-hard-by-donald-trumps-reciprocal-tariffs-heres-why-7708057%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Briton%20dead%20and%20three%20injured%20in%20New%20Zealand%20crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739515680000%2C%22visua