ine%2C%20largely%20because%20the%20call%20was%20held%20before%20Trump%20officially%20spoke%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d20c997c-dfe0-4f08-b069-feaf818f9d51%5C%22%3E'Let's%20get%20it%20done'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20published%20details%20about%20the%20call%20with%20Putin%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113991956474899296%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20TruthSocial.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20wrote%20that%20the%20pair%20had%20%26quot%3Bagreed%20to%20work%20together%2C%20very%20closely%26quot%3B%20and%20planned%20to%20visit%20each%20other's%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20sparked%20fears%20in%20Europe%20and%20Ukraine%20that%20the%20US%20may%20try%20to%20negotiate%20an%20end%20to%20the%20war%20without%20their%20input%2C%20prompting%20European%20leaders%20to%20insist%20on%20Thursday%20that%20they%20need%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20an%20agreement%20made%20behind%20our%20backs%2C%20it%20will%20simply%20not%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaja%20Kallas%2C%20the%20top%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20European%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20later%20said%20that%20Trump%20called%20him%20too%2C%20and%20that%20the%20American%20president%20shared%20details%20about%20his%20conversation%20with%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20wants%20peace%20more%20than%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelenskyy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FZelenskyyUa%2Fstatus%2F1889737480892719552%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BTogether%20with%20the%20US%2C%20we%20are%20charting%20our%20next%20steps%20to%20stop%20Russian%20aggression%20and%20ensure%20a%20lasting%2C%20reliable%20peace.%20As%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20let's%20get%20it%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Russia%2C%20officials%20signaled%20elation%20at%20the%20Trump-P