2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shivon%20Zilis%20Joins%20Elon%20Musk%20During%20Meet%20With%20PM%20Modi.%20Who%20Is%20She%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20US%2C%20was%20accompanied%20by%20his%20partner%20Shivon%20Zilis%20and%20their%20two%20children%20-%20Azure%20and%20Strider%20(twins)%20and%20X%20(who%20Mr%20Musk%20had%20with%20his%20ex-partner%20Grimes)%20-%20to%20the%20meeting%20at%20Blair%20House%20in%20Washington.%20Shivon%20Zilis%2C%20a%20top%20employee%20at%20Elon%20Musk's%20brain%20chip%20startup%20Neuralink%2C%20has%20stayed%20largely%20out%20of%20the%20spotlight%20over%20the%20years.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20such%20appearance%20she%20made%20alongside%20Mr%20Musk%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Shivon%20Zilis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivon%20Zilis%2C%2039%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Canada%20and%20is%20reportedly%20a%20Yale%20University%20graduate.%20Her%20mother%2C%20Sharda%20N%2C%20is%20Indian%2C%20while%20her%20father%2C%20Richard%20Zilis%20is%20Canadian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Zilis%20works%20as%20the%20director%20of%20operations%20and%20special%20projects%20at%20Neuralink.%20She%20worked%20as%20a%20project%20director%20for%20Tesla%20between%202017%20to%202019.%20She%20has%20also%20been%20an%20advisor%20to%20Sam%20Altman's%20OpenAI%20and%20has%20been%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20investment%20team%20at%20Bloomberg%20Beta%20where%20she%20led%20as%20many%20as%20nine%20investments%20since%20its%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Ms%20Zilis%20was%20listed%20on%20the%20Forbes%2030%20Under%2030%20list%20of%20venture%20capitalists.%20She%20was%20also%20named%20among%20LinkedIn's%2035%20Under%2035.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Zilis%20is%20known%20to%20be%20Mr%20Musk's%20present%20partner.%20The%20two%20welcomed%20two%20children%2C%20Azure%20and%20Strider%2C%20in%202021%20-%20the%20same%20year%20when%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20had%20his%20second%20child%20with%20Grimes.%20In%202024%2C%20Ms%20Zilis%20and%20Mr%20Musk%20had%20a%20third%20child%20together.%20While%20the%20duo%20never%20officially%20acknowledged%20their%20relationship%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20Ms%20Zilis%20had%20moved%20into%20the%20Texas%20compound%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20built%20for%20all%20his%2011%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20were%20seen%20together%20in%20November%20last%20year%20while%20attending%20a%20gala%20together%20at%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20Mar-A-Lago%20estate.%20She%20stayed%20in%20the%20background%20as%20Mr%20Musk%20posed%20with%20their%20daughter%20Azure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20Modi-Elon%20Musk%20meeting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20met%20Elon%20Musk%20hours%20before%20his%20meeting%20with%20President%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20According%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20the%20two%20duo%20discussed%20key%20topics%20such%20as%20space%2C%20mobility%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20innovation.%20They%20also%20reportedly%20discussed%20strengthening%20collaboration%20between%20Indian%20and%20US%20entities%20in%20innovation%2C%20space%20exploration%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20sustainable%20development%2C%20and%20also%20opportunities%20to%20deepen%20cooperation%20in%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20good%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20at%20Blair%20House%2C%20PM%20Modi%20gifted%20the%20Musk%20children%20three%20books%20-%20The%20Crescent%20Moon%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20The%20Great%20RK%20Narayan%20Collection%2C%20and%20Pandit%20Vishnu%20Sharma's%20Panchatantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20shared%20pictures%20of%20the%20meeting%20in%20which%20Mr%20Musk's%20children%20can%20be%20seen%20reading%20the%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20a%20delight%20to%20meet%20Mr%20Elon%20Musk's%20family%20and%20to%20talk%20about%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20subjects%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Musk%20-%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%20in%20the%20Trump%20regime%20-%20have%20met%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past.%20In%202015%2C%20PM%20Modi%20visited%20the%20Tesla%20facility%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20where%20he%20was%20given%20a%20personal%20tour%20by%20the%20Tesla%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739513760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Frcibcrmg_shivon-zilis_625x300_14_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-shivon-zilis-woman-seen-with-elon-musk-when-he-met-pm-modi-7707007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20latter's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20was%20accompanied%20by%20his%20partner%20Shivon%20Zilis%20and%20their%20three%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-shivon-zilis-woman-seen-with-elon-musk-when-he-met-pm-modi-7707007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20Goes%20To%20Supreme%20Court%20Over%20FIRs%20In%20Different%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%2C%20widely%20known%20by%20his%20online%20moniker%20%26quot%3BBeerBiceps%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20relief%20against%20multiple%20FIRs%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20various%20states.%20The%20FIRs%20stem%20from%20controversial%20remarks%20made%20during%20a%20now-deleted%20YouTube%20reality%20show%2C%20India's%20Got%20Latent%2C%20hosted%20by%20comedian%20Samay%20Raina.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Allahbadia%2C%20through%20his%20lawyer%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20to%20club%20together%20the%20FIRs%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20different%20states.%20The%20YouTuber%20also%20sought%20anticipatory%20bail%2C%20fearing%20arrest%20by%20the%20Guwahati%20police%2C%20who%20have%20already%20issued%20summons%20to%20him%20and%20others%20involved%20in%20the%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20requested%20an%20early%20hearing%2C%20which%20was%20mentioned%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna.%20However%2C%20the%20CJI%20declined%20to%20grant%20an%20immediate%20hearing%2C%20stating%20that%20a%20date%20had%20already%20been%20assigned%20for%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20advised%20Mr%20Allahbadia's%20legal%20team%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20registry%20for%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20made%20remarks%20about%20parents%20and%20sex%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20India's%20Got%20Latent%2C%20a%20reality%20show%20that%20featured%20comedians%20and%20influencers%20as%20judges%20and%20participants.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%20watch%20your%20parents%20have%20sex%20every%20day%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life%20or%20join%20in%20once%20and%20stop%20it%20forever%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%2C%20deemed%20offensive%20by%20many%2C%20led%20to%20widespread%20outrage%20and%20multiple%20complaints%20across%20the%20country.%20A%20resident%20of%20Guwahati%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint%2C%20prompting%20the%20Assam%20police%20to%20register%20a%20case%20under%20sections%20related%20to%20obscenity%20and%20public%20morality.%20The%20case%20names%20Mr%20Allahbadia%2C%20Mr%20Raina%2C%20and%20other%20participants%2C%20including%20Ashish%20Chanchlani%2C%20Jaspreet%20Singh%2C%20and%20Apoorva%20Makhija.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIRs%20against%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20and%20others%2C%20including%20Mr%20Raina%2C%20were%20filed%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20Assam%2C%20following%20complaints%20about%20alleged%20obscenity%20and%20crass%20remarks%20made%20during%20the%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20police%20team%20is%20currently%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20serve%20summons%20to%20Mr%20Allahbadia%2C%20Mr%20Raina%2C%20and%20other%20participants.%20Mr%20Raina%2C%20who%20resides%20in%20Pune%2C%20has%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Assam%20police%20within%20four%20days.%20However%2C%20the%20comedian%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20United%20States%20for%20his%20shows%20and%20has%20sought%20additional%20time%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20even%20reached%20the%20halls%20of%20Parliament%2C%20where%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Naresh%20Mhaske%20raised%20the%20issue%2C%20calling%20for%20stricter%20regulations%20on%20social%20media%20content.%20A%20parliamentary%20panel%20on%20communications%20and%20information%20technology%20has%20asked%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20to%20submit%20a%20detailed%20note%20on%20the%20matter%20by%20February%2017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739513340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Flcmofocg_ranveer-allahbadia-_625x300_10_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutuber-ranveer-allahbadia-goes-to-supreme-court-over-firs-against-him-in-different-states-7707440%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22YouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%2C%20widely%20known%20by%20his%20online%20moniker%20%26quot%3BBeerBiceps%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20relief%20against%20multiple%20FIRs%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20various%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutuber-ranveer-allahbadia-goes-to-supreme-court-over-firs-against-him-in-different-states-7707440%22%2C%22cdnAm