%20was%20glued%20to%20the%20India%20coach%20throughout%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20faced%20BCCI's%20ire%20after%20the%20tour.%20The%20board%20is%20keen%20to%20not%20let%20the%20same%20happen%20during%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Dubai.%20It%20has%20been%20reported%20that%20the%20PA%20is%20now%20staying%20at%20a%20different%20hotel%20than%20the%20one%20where%20the%20team%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20personal%20secretary%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20coaching%20staff%2C%20who%20was%20regularly%20seen%20staying%20at%20the%20team%20hotel%2C%20now%20stays%20at%20a%20different%20facility%20even%20though%20he%20has%20been%20seen%20at%20every%20venue%20during%20the%20England%20home%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PTI%20report%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20was%20the%20only%20coaching%20staff%20during%20the%20Australia%20tour%20who%20had%20a%20personal%20assistant.%20The%20coach%20can%20no%20longer%20have%20the%20same%20setup%2C%20as%20the%20board%20has%20officially%20enforced%20its%20new%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20his%20PA%20sitting%20in%20the%20car%20specified%20for%20national%20selectors%3F%20They%20can't%20even%20discuss%20things%20in%20private%20with%20an%20unknown%20third%20person%20in%20the%20car.%20Why%20was%20he%20allotted%20space%20in%20the%20BCCI's%20hospitality%20box%20in%20Adelaide%3F%26quot%3B%20an%20irritated%20BCCI%20official%20had%20told%20the%20news%20agency%20after%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaks%20from%20the%20Indian%20dressing%20room%20have%20become%20quite%20common%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20Even%20during%20the%20Australia%20tour%2C%20there%20were%20a%20few%20'leaks'%20that%20became%20public.%20The%20board%20seems%20to%20be%20keen%20to%20reduce%20such%20'leaks'%20by%20not%20allowing%20any%20unauthorised%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20did%20he%20have%20breakfast%20in%20the%20cordoned-off%20area%20of%20a%20five-star%20facility%20that%20is%20just%20earmarked%20for%20the%20team%20members%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20official%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20BCCI%20diktat%2C%20the%20players%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20have%20their%20family%20members%2C%20wives%20or%20partners%20accompany%20them%20during%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20In%20a%20case%20where%20an%20exception%20is%20made%2C%20the%20player%20would%20himself%20have%20to%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20family's%20travel.%20Such%20measures%20weren't%20apparently%20in%20place%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20has%20also%20put%20restrictions%20on%20personal%20chefs%2C%20hair%20stylists%20and%20agents%20of%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739510100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fpu5q5kj_gautam-gambhir-bcci_625x300_10_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsetback-for-gautam-gambhir-as-bcci-enforces-new-rules-coach-given-no-exception-report-7707216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20given%20no%20exception%20as%20the%20BCCI%20enforced%20its%20new%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsetback-for-gautam-gambhir-as-bcci-enforces-new-rules-coach-given-no-exception-report-7707216%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Phone%203a%20series%20will%20be%20powered%20by%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%2C%20confirms%20Nothing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739509823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fphone-3a-series-will-be-powered-by-qualcomm-snapdragon-confirms-nothing-125021400566_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nothing%20has%20used%20Qualcomm%20chips%20for%20its%20flagship%20number%20series%2C%20but%20last%20year's%20A-series%20models%20featured%20MediaTek%20Dimensity%20chipsets%22%2C%22aut